n有無辦法搵外媒搵個機師出黎講<br />\n仲有公開無線電通訊錄音<br />\n搞到支那籍飛機限制入美國領空就足以收晒支那黨企航空皮"},{"pid":"9a325b8da610393a3580a648deebaac61c9607df","tid":1791293,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T17:03:51.000Z","msg":"冇人講？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}